body.value: <font color="lightgrey">as a specific kind of action, and to personalize it in a way that perhaps makes sense to us. One of the-- one of my firmest beliefs is that no one ever thought of herself as a slave. That 'slave' was not anyone's name or job title or, or any other such thing that, that people were persons first, in their own mind's eye and their own imagination prior to anything else.</font>
